    {
      "id": "port-contract-optional",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Optional Structure",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -60,
        "y": 40
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Optional Structure\n\nA port contract MAY additionally declare:\n\n- semantic type taxonomy such as `text`, `control`, `data`, `graph_ref`, or domain-specific types\n- multiplicity such as `one` or `many`\n- explicit wildcard policy\n- default root handling\n- migration notes and human stewardship notes\n\nOptional fields may refine meaning, but they must never backdoor new authority.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
