    {
      "id": "port-contract-forbidden",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Forbidden States",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 440,
        "y": 40
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Forbidden States\n\nThe following states are invalid:\n\n- bridge or runtime authority inferred from a rendered card or view\n- omitted compatibility treated as permissive\n- wildcard behavior guessed instead of declared\n- semantic type mismatches silently tolerated\n- visual affordance treated as class authority\n\nWhen the contract is underspecified, the safe outcome is downgrade or refusal.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
