    {
      "id": "port-contract-portability",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Portability",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 680,
        "y": 470
      },
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Portability\n\nPort meaning must survive transport between graphs, repos, and hosts.\n\nDocument explicit, reversible evolution for:\n\n- authority ladder changes\n- semantic type renames\n- multiplicity changes\n- default root policy changes\n- boundary filtering behavior\n\nPortability requires stable ids, explicit versions, and no hidden escalations.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "definitionKey": "markdown",
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "port-contract-declaration"
