    {
      "id": "port-contract-examples",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Examples",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -60,
        "y": 880
      },
      "width": 470,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Examples\n\n**Valid:**\n- host.navigate_port -> target.root\n- host.consume_view -> target.port_view\n- bridge authority granted only through an explicit bridge-mode contract\n\n**Invalid (must fail):**\n- bridge authority inferred from a rendered card\n- runtime behavior granted because a target view happens to exist\n- incompatible semantic types connected without explicit wildcard policy",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
