    {
      "id": "port-contract-references",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "References",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 460,
        "y": 880
      },
      "width": 470,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## References\n\nRelated authorities and walkthroughs:\n\n- Contracts index for neighboring laws\n- Bridge contract for import authority\n- Edge contract for relationship transport and validation\n- Port primitive tutorial for hands-on authoring\n\nUse these together when designing ports that expose surfaces across graph boundaries.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "definitionKey": "markdown",
        "identity": {
