    {
      "id": "port-contract-metadata",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Metadata Note",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 980,
        "y": 880
      },
      "width": 470,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Metadata Note\n\nEvery normative port contract should declare schema-level metadata such as:\n\n- **Port ID:** stable contract identifier\n- **Contract Version:** explicit `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`\n- **Status:** `experimental | stable | deprecated`\n- **Defined In:** canonical graph or source path\n\nMetadata keeps validation, migration, and stewardship from relying on guesswork.",
